h EphA2 in insect cells and optimizing purification protocols. I'll apply docking simulations to predict how sterile alpha motif (SAM) domain positioning might create allosteric pockets. Dr. Robert Stahelin (Medicinal Chemistry and Molecular Pharmacology) provides ITC training as I validate ligand binding in different phosphomutants."
